divs: Sighting DetailsMarch 10,2012 at 8-9 PM,dark outside.Outside smoking again,then i saw 5-6 small lights flew towards south.They were weak,almost transparent.They flew almost beside each other,in tree height.They was ca 10-15 meters above the ground.No sound.
Summary: Saw 5-6 small lights flew right above me.
